snippet.title: Judge Absolutely Humiliates Amber Heard Team After Court, They Can't Add Up!
snippet.description:
Elaine Elaine Elaine Bredehoft, please, no more, I can't take it. Judge Penny crushes you after court because you cannot add up. Utter humiliation yet again. Amber Heard will not be happy, but Johnny Depp will. Enjoy this extra nugget of pure comedy gold from the defamation trial in Virginia.

https://youtu.be/XVO7Jv2w1kA

Trial day 7 
https://youtu.be/RCV-dNClAww --- Johnny Depp testifies against Amber Heard
Trial day 8 https://youtu.be/j5wVWMbh2W4 --- Johnny testifies and start of cross examination
